			<header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard">
				<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b5383c42761246f20ab7db9c5f8866b1?s=44&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b5383c42761246f20ab7db9c5f8866b1?s=88&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' loading='lazy' decoding='async'/><cite><b class="fn"><a href="https://archive.org/details/fav-daniel_sauers?sort=-addeddate" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Daniel Sauers</a></b> </cite><a href="https://blog.archive.org/2023/03/25/the-fight-continues/#comment-432887"><time datetime="2023-04-02T07:39:46+00:00">April 2, 2023 at 7:39 am</time></a>				</header><!-- .comment-meta -->

				
				
