<p>Ethics??? HA!</p>
<p>We have time and time again seen that corporations will try to get away with murder if there&#8217;s a buck in it for them. If it was legal, or if there was legal loopholes that made it likely for a corporate entity to want to try and make a profit off of it, you betcha it would only be a matter of time before an corporation would chop your grandmother up, can her remains and sell her as fishbait.</p>
<p>If you think this isn&#8217;t the case, and if you don&#8217;t think there&#8217;s a battle on to wring every single dollar out of whoever has a dollar on their pockets, every single last fraction of a percent of potential profit margin off the markets (white, grey, or otherwise) in any way possible, then you are the terribly historically ignorant child here and you should go sit in the corner with reddened cheeks.</p>
<p>-p</p>
