				<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bbcdda567cd5830b4d8185e2e4ae9344?s=44&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bbcdda567cd5830b4d8185e2e4ae9344?s=88&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' loading='lazy' decoding='async'/><cite><b class="fn">Queuenard</b> </cite><a href="https://blog.archive.org/2023/03/25/the-fight-continues/#comment-432498"><time datetime="2023-03-29T04:24:36+00:00">March 29, 2023 at 4:24 am</time></a>				</header><!-- .comment-meta -->

				
				
