				<p>Will the Internet Archive be transparent to its donors about censorship on the Internet Archive library and Wayback Machine? Will there ever be a list of items restricted with &#8220;You must log in to view this content&#8221;? You claim to be worried about &#8220;[holding] back access to information&#8221; but yet you are putting up barriers like these? Are you a library or just an extension of big tech operating under false premise of fighting such?</p>
